item.title: Exclusive Engagement
item.description: This is a clubber’s dream full of new House, Hip Hop, and remixes, plus a bunch of tracks that I am feeling. The track-list you can see at www.choycekutz.com. I hope you enjoy the mixtape and feel free to hit me with an email or leave a comment.

item.title: Handcuffed Dj's Vol. 3
item.description: This is a mixtape I did about 3 months ago. A straight hype party style tape with Hip Hop and Dancehall all the way through it. Pop this in on the way to the club and you will come out wanting to hear it again. Podshow PDN {podshow-f3fa834e5b8fae52ee3511071a4c5aa3}

item.title: We Ride, Me and My B
item.description: This is a smooth tape that you and your girl will both love. A mixture of Hip Hop, Reggae, Remixes, as well as new and classic R&B. Names like Timberland, Rhianna, Mr. Easy, Young Joc, SWV, and many more. Put it in relax and it will keep you head nodding.
